column5: "Making a sword out of wood wasn't the smartest idea ever. This is more of a club than a sword..."
"This is an iron sword. How generic!"
"This is a steel sword. How generic!"
"This is a mithril sword. This is slightly less generic!"
"This is a rune sword. This is slightly less generic!"
"You could sell this and get something more effective..."
"You really should sell this."
"Where did someone get enough obsidian to make a sword?"
"What? Why would anyone actually use this?"
"Making a shield out of wood wasn't the smartest idea ever. I hope you don't try to block firebolts..."
"This is an iron shield. How generic!"
"This is a steel shield. How generic (and heavy)!"
"This is a mithril shield. This is slightly less generic!"
"This is a rune shield. This is slightly less generic!"
"This is a giant chunk of gold and you're trying to use it to block attacks. Reevaluate your choices."
"This is a giant chunk of diamond and you're trying to use it to block attacks. Reevaluate your choices."
"This came straight out of a volcano. Neat."
"I don't think you can block more than one attack with this..."
"These are more effective at making you look like a wood elf than they are at protecting you."
"These are iron shoulder guards. How generic!"
"These are steel shoulder guards. How generic!"
"These are mithril shoulder guards. These are slightly less generic!"
"These are rune shoulder guards. These are slightly less generic!"
"These are gold shoulder guards. These are expensive!"
"These are diamond shoulder guards. These are very expensive!"
"These are obsidian shoulder guards."
"These are glass shoulder guards."
"This is more effective at making you look like a wood elf than it is at protecting you."
"This is an iron chestplate. How generic!"
"This is a steel chestplate. How generic (and heavy)!"
"This is a mithril chestplate. This is slightly less generic!"
"This is a rune chestplate. This is slightly less generic!"
"This is a gold chestplate."
"This is a diamond chestplate."
"This is an obsidian chestplate. It smells like fire and brimstone."
"Wear this to maximize bodily injury upon attack."
"These are more effective at making you look like a wood elf than they are at protecting you."
"These are iron leg guards. How generic!"
"These are steel leg guards. How generic!"
"These are mithril leg guards. These are slightly less generic!"
"These are rune leg guards. These are slightly less generic!"
"These are gold leg guards. These are expensive!"
"These are diamond leg guards. These are very expensive!"
"These are obsidian leg guards."
"It would be a shame if these shattered."
"You can't move your hands while wearing these."
"These are iron gauntlets. How generic!"
"These are steel gauntlets. How generic!"
"These are mithril gauntlets. These are slightly less generic!"
"These are rune gauntlets. These are slightly less generic!"
"These are gold gauntlets."
"These are diamond gauntlets."
"These are obsidian gauntlets."
"Caution: fragile. Handle with care."
"You'll sound like a horse if you run while wearing these."
"These are iron boots. How generic!"
"These are steel boots. How generic!"
"These are mithril boots. These are slightly less generic!"
"These are rune boots. These are slightly less generic!"
"When you're so rich that you can step on gold."
"When you're so rich that you can step on diamond."
"Lava walkers"
"Ouch, tread lightly."
"Is it a helmet or a bowl? The world may never know."
"For when you want to look like a welder..."
"Putting this much strain on your neck is probably a bad idea."
"This is a mithril helm. This is slightly less generic!"
"This is a rune helm. This is slightly less generic!"
"When you aren't sure if you want a crown or a helmet, get this."
"If you're wearing a giant chunk of diamond to protect your head, you probably already took a significant blow to the head."
"This is an obsidian helm."
"Use this only if you want shards in your eye."
"This is hardly a dagger..."
"This is an iron dagger. How generic!"
"This is a steel dagger. How generic!"
"This is a mithril dagger. This is slightly less generic!"
"This is a rune dagger. This is slightly less generic!"
"If you can afford to stab someone with gold, you could probably just hire someone to do the job..."
"If you can afford to stab someone with diamond, you could probably just hire someone to do the job..."
"For when you have a volcanic fury."
"Single use only."
"This is a shrinkwrapped fork. Wow!"
"An alien artifact from a galaxy far, far away?"
"This device fires landsharks. You read that right."
"User beware: momentum is conserved."
"Legolas would be proud."
"This doesn't fire bolts of lightning, but it'll work."
"For piercing armor at long range."
"For piercing armor at short range."
"This is a curved sword."
"For use on trees only."
"You might mistake it for a magical staff, but this is nothing more than a walking stick."
"This is a stick that has been imbued with magical properties."
"A slight glow is emanating from the blade.'
"For use on grass only."
"This is an iron mace. How generically medieval."
"And my axe!"
"This is a spiked hammer."
"Here is a test description."
"Use this when you really mean business."
